Hello! I’m Yasniel, and together with my wife, we're thrilled to share our selection of high-quality vehicles with both travelers and Miami locals. As small business owners and parents of three wonderful children, we understand the importance of reliability, comfort, and excellent customer service.

Having lived in Miami, FL for over 15 years, we’ve come to love and appreciate the vibrant culture and dynamic energy of this city. We are passionate about travel and often take road trips as a family, experiences that have given us insight into what makes a rental experience exceptional.

We take immense pride in our fleet of cars, ensuring each one is well-maintained and ready to provide you with a seamless travel experience. Whether you’re visiting to explore the beautiful sights of Miami or a local in need of a temporary ride, we’re here to make your journey enjoyable and hassle-free.

Connect with us! We’d love to share recommendations for exploring Miami or to hear about your travel experiences. Let's make your next car rental experience memorable!
I want you to have the best experience, And that you can enjoy all of Miami in our luxury vehicles, With our best attention. 🙌
